          "074aed08-271d-4f2b-869f-1e2e869fdba5": "float4 noise = hash41u(vertexIndex);\nfloat3 pos = v.Position;\nfloat4 f = GetField( float4(pos, 0));\nfloat4 fColor = GetField( float4(pos, 1));\n\nv.Position +=  A * (noise - 0.5) * f.w;\n\nfloat4 c= Gradient.SampleLevel(Sampler, float2(f.w * C, 0.5), 0);\nv.ColorRGB= c.rgb;\n"
