          "074aed08-271d-4f2b-869f-1e2e869fdba5": "// A: Falloff\n// B: Size\n\nfloat4 noise = hash41u(vertexIndex);\nfloat3 pos = v.Position;\nfloat d = GetField( float4(pos, 0)).w;\n\nfloat f = Biased(smoothstep(1,0,(d-A) / B));\nv.ColorRGB = SampleGradient(f);\n"
